<div id="review_1891833571" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1891833571" />
    <a title="Kathleen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/56509454-kathleen"><img alt="Kathleen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1502640116p2/56509454.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1891833571?book_show_action=true">Mar 18, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kathleen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kathleen" href="/user/show/56509454-kathleen">Kathleen</a>
      </span>

          added it


          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781503941144" href="/book/show/30848544-in-the-light-of-the-garden">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56509454-kathleen?shelf=read-in-2017">read-in-2017</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56509454-kathleen?shelf=read-ebook">read-ebook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56509454-kathleen?shelf=subscription">subscription</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56509454-kathleen?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56509454-kathleen?shelf=2017-book-challenge-completed">2017-book-challenge-completed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56509454-kathleen?shelf=sub-once-upon-a-time-book-club">sub-once-upon-a-time-book-club</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1891833571" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9705901211716064214">This just wasn&apos;t my cup of tea. I think the Once Upon a Time Book Club subscription is a charming idea and obviously those who run it put a lot of time into it, but I get really annoyed with chick lit books where everyone is supposedly damaged but when we meet them things start magically working out for them. I suppose I should have known that a subscription named &quot;Once Upon a Time&quot; would choose some fairy tale stories and this book is no exception. There&apos;s nothing wrong with it if you&apos;re lookin</span>
  <span id="freeText9705901211716064214" style="display:none">This just wasn't my cup of tea. I think the Once Upon a Time Book Club subscription is a charming idea and obviously those who run it put a lot of time into it, but I get really annoyed with chick lit books where everyone is supposedly damaged but when we meet them things start magically working out for them. I suppose I should have known that a subscription named "Once Upon a Time" would choose some fairy tale stories and this book is no exception. There's nothing wrong with it if you're looking to escape reality and indulge in the fantasy for a bit. I wouldn't have chosen it for myself if not for the book club, so I hesitate to give it a star rating when it just wasn't for me.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9705901211716064214" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


